3.23.2 - Nov 21, 2016
=====================

Changes since 3.22.0:

- All fixes in 3.22.1, 3.22.2 and 3.22.3.
- Allow sending CTRL+ALT+F3 key combo to guest (for reaching TTY3) shortcut.
- Don't autosave live & under-installation VMs.
- Use new Gtk+ CSS property names.
- Re-layout custom osinfo db to comply with new libosinfo format.
- Use latest libgd.
- Fix some user-visible strings.
- Allow redirection of USB mouse and keyboard if 'BOXES_USB_REDIR_ALL'
  environment variable is set.
- Make use of unicode in translatable strings.
- Added/updated/fixed translations:
  - Catalan
  - Chinese (Taiwan)
  - Czech
  - Finnish
  - French
  - Friulian
  - German
  - Hungarian
  - Italian
  - Norwegian bokmål
  - Polish
  - Spanish

