3.19.3 - Dec 16, 2015
=====================

Changes since 3.19.1:

- On restoring a libvirt VM from saved state, try to sync the guest clock with
  host clock. This requires Qemu guest agent in the VM.
- Keyboard shorcuts:
  - Add shortcuts help window.
  - Fix shortcuts for RTL locales.
  - Drop alt+a shortcut.
- Add kudos in appdata file.
- Added/updated/fixed translations:
  - Finnish
  - Hebrew
  - Hungarian
  - Kazakh
  - Lithuanian
  - Norwegian bokmål
  - Portuguese
  - Slovak
  - Spanish
  - Swedish

Dependencies changed:

- Require gtk+ >= 3.19.4
- Require libvirt-glib >= 0.2.3

